item.title: Lets get this huga business started
item.description: Why am I here? Going to have a look at what kind of markdown Hugo supports. Can they do lists and sub items what about check boxes yep this is done First Second Third Can we do table of contents? [[TOC]] does not work? Or even some basic links. using Bananas; namespace Split { publi class Peel { } } Invoke-psake Bananas -token '@#$'
